==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pyoid
<hw>Py"oid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ pus +
-<ets>-oid</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to pus;
of the nature of, or like, pus.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Pyoid corpuscles</b></col> <fld>(Med.)</fld>, <cd>cells
of a size larger than pus corpuscles, containing two or more of the
latter.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pyopneumothorax</ent>⟦br⟧
